    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"276071\">@Nathaniel Virgo</span> Thanks! That gives me a bunch of stuff to chew on. Unfortunately I don't understand double categories yet, but I've just started reading about internal categories and hopefully i can move from there to double categories</p>",
